<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="now-adv">now <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /naʊ/    美 /naʊ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[表示时间段] 现在；目前：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I suppose he has arrived in Beijing <strong>by now</strong>.
我想他现在已经到北京了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It is quite difficult now to find a person without a cell phone. 
现在很难找到没有手机的人。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>[表示时间点] 立刻；马上：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Start writing now. 
马上开始写吧。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>[表示话题转换]：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Now, open your books to page 15. 
现在，打开书翻到15页。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="every-now-and-then-again">(every) now and then / again</h3>
<p>1.<strong>时而；偶尔：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Snakes come near the house now and then. 
时不时会有蛇爬到房子附近。</p><footer>人教⑧ – 3</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Now and again he still visits me. 
他偶尔还来看我。</p></div>

<h3 id="for-now">for now</h3>
<p>1.<strong>目前；暂时：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Although these measures are not effective forever, they are vital for now.
尽管这些措施不会永远有效，但目前还是极为重要的。</p><footer>2016 北京</footer></div>

<h3 id="from-now-on">from now on</h3>
<p>1.<strong>从现在起：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>From now on, I'll pay more attention to my health father than my weight.
从现在开始，我会更注重我的健康而不是体重。</p><footer>译林新必修① – 4</footer></div>

<h3 id="just-now">just now</h3>
<p>1.<strong>刚才；现在：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Tom was here just now. 
汤姆刚才在这儿的。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Do not talk about it just now. 
现在别讨论这件事。</p></div>

<h3 id="up-to-now-until-now-till-now">up to now / until now / till now</h3>
<p>1.<strong>迄今为止：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Up to / Until now, the program has saved thousands of children who would otherwise have died.
到目前为止，这项计划已经挽救了成千上万名原本会死亡的那些孩子。</p><footer>2010 山东</footer></div></div>